en_802935_0	In order to motivate Commando Regiment (CR) achievers in national / international and para sports competitions as well as to felicitate some of those who have turned disabled having contributed to those victories, a get-together was organized recently in the CR Regimental Headquarters.
en_802935_1	Brigadier H.H.A.S.P.K Senarathna, Director Plans, Army Headquarters attended the event as the Chief Guest.
en_802935_2	Retired Commanding Officers, retired Regimental Sergeant Majors, disabled CR soldiers joined the evening.
